{"talk":{"id":2472,"name":"Dan Gross: Why gun violence can't be our new normal","description":"It doesn't matter whether you love or hate guns; it's obvious that the US would be a safer place if there weren't thousands of them sold every day without background checks. Dan Gross, president of the Brady Campaign to Prevent Gun Violence, makes a passionate, personal appeal for something that more than 90 percent of Americans want: background checks for all gun sales. \"For every great movement around the world, there's a moment where you can look back and say, 'That's when things really started to change,'\" Gross says. \"For the movement to end gun violence in America, that moment is here.\"","slug":"dan_gross_why_gun_violence_can_t_be_our_new_normal","recorded_at":"2016-02-17 00:00:00","published_at":"2016-03-29 14:58:52","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:46:59","viewed_count":1244655,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":377,"name":"TED2016"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/65c974e81011899f667e9c6393b4a101be314643_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/65c974e81011899f667e9c6393b4a101be314643_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/65c974e81011899f667e9c6393b4a101be314643_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/65c974e81011899f667e9c6393b4a101be314643_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9a63066f547849409c1a997fc0c3ed42099ef324_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DanGross_2016-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6742703,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DanGross_2016-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":18720419,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DanGro